Creative Commons Attribution V4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)

The Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0) 
license is the primary license that requires attribution but 
nothing else. It allows others to distribute, remix, tweak, 
and build upon a work—even commercially—as long as they 
credit the original creator.
- https://creativecommons.org/share-your-work/cclicenses/

The authors of each data set will be listed with the data set.
